sentences.english: Cytokines are small, soluble proteins with pleiotropic effects on a variety of cell types.
sentences.chinese: 细胞因子是具有多种生物活性的可溶性小分子蛋白质。

sentences.english: Interleukin 10 is a pleiotropic cytokine produced by many cells in human.
sentences.chinese: 素10是由多种细胞产生的多效细胞因子。

sentences.english: Objective: To investigate the distribution of cytokine gene polymorphisms.
sentences.chinese: 目的探讨细胞因子基因多态性分布。

sentences.english: Adipose tissue has been shown capable of expressing proinflammatory cytokines.
sentences.chinese: 脂肪组织能表达促炎细胞因子。

sentences.english: Result There is no obvious difference between the two experimental groups as to the blood routine test, but cytokines show significantly different.
sentences.chinese: 结果两组血常规无明显差异，细胞因子差异有显著性。

sentences.english: Tumor necrosis factor (TNF)- alpha is one of the cytokines which the fatty tissue secretes.
sentences.chinese: 是脂肪组织分泌的多种细胞因子之一。

sentences.english: Cytokines such as TNF may prevent transcription of the thrombomodulin gene.
sentences.chinese: TNF等细胞因子可阻止凝血调节因子基因的转录。

sentences.english: Can I save the remaining cytokine standard for next time use?
sentences.chinese: 我能保存剩余的细胞因子标准品用于下一次实验吗？

sentences.english: Objective To study the effect of Zhongyao Fuzheng Mixture(ZFM)on cytokines in tumor model mice.
sentences.chinese: 目的研究中药扶正合剂对肿瘤模型细胞因子的影响。

sentences.english: Chemokines are chemotactic cytokines that can direct cells trafficking, conducting their functions via chemokine receptors.
sentences.chinese: 趋化因子是一类控制细胞定向迁移的细胞因子。

sentences.english: Conclusion The disorder of cellular factor network may participate in the pathogenesis of AA.
sentences.chinese: 结论细胞因子网络失调在再障发病中起一定作用。

sentences.english: The expression of cytokines in aqueous humor was almost consistent with the process of inflammation.
sentences.chinese: 各细胞因子在房水中的表达变化基本与炎症进程相符。

sentences.english: No cytokine release syndrome was observed and only 2 cases of DGF.
sentences.chinese: 未出现细胞因子释放综合征，仅2例DGF。

sentences.english: This article summarizes the progress of tumor treatment with cytokine.
sentences.chinese: 本文简要概述了用细胞因子治疗肿瘤方面的进展。

sentences.english: Is there any cross-reactivity between the cytokines?
sentences.chinese: 细胞因子之间会有交叉反应吗？

sentences.english: The hematopoietic cells were cocultivated with concentrated virus supernatant and interleukins.
sentences.chinese: 骨髓造血细胞与浓缩病毒上清及细胞因子组合共培养。
